    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.瞭解進階燈光系統之工程圖設計。<br>2.具備基礎電學配電理論。<br>3.深入光學色彩設計應用能力。<br>4.發展進階舞台燈光設計光學色彩學。<br>5.進階舞台燈光設計。<br>6.室內與戶外演唱會執行。<br><br><br>",
        "en": "1. Understand the engineering drawing design of advanced lighting system.<br>2. Possess basic electrical power distribution theory.<br>3. In-depth optical color design application capabilities.<br>4. Develop advanced stage lighting design optical color science.<br>5. Advanced stage lighting design.<br>6. Perform indoor and outdoor concerts."
